        "content": "## Atlas Platform — Observability Baseline\n\n**Prometheus** (green = UP): Prometheus is running and scraping itself successfully. The monitoring infrastructure is operational.\n\n**atlas-portal / orion-api / airflow** (orange = Not instrumented): These services do not yet expose a `/metrics` endpoint in Prometheus text format. Prometheus scrape attempts fail, so `up=0` for these targets. This is expected for Phase 1.\n\n**Phase 2 — app instrumentation (next step):**\n- Add `prom-client` to `atlas-portal` → exposes `/metrics` with HTTP request rate, latency, process metrics\n- Add `prometheus-fastapi-instrumentator` to `orion-api` → exposes `/metrics` automatically\n- Once instrumented, panels above turn green and HTTP metrics panels can be added to this dashboard",
